topic: Sport Workflow Series (Basketball and NBA seasons explorative search")

goals.1: Identify the BGP for basketball player.
goals.3: Identify the BGP for basketball team.
goals.4: Return all french basketball teams born before 1930 (the result set must be a list of triples basketball team IRI, label and year of inception).
goals.5: Return all the NBA season (the result set must be a list of couples NBA season IRI, label)
goals.6: Consider only the basketball teams which Michael Jordan and Kobe Bryant played. Return the number of NBA seasons won by these teams (the result set must be a list of triples basketball team IRI, label and #victories. Return a number for each basketball team even if they never won a season).
goals.7: Consider only NBA (National Basketball Association) basketball teams and all basketball players who played in one of these teams at least once. Also consider the country of citizenship of the players with the related continent. Return for each continent the number of players who played in an NBA basketball teams. (the result set must be triples of continent IRI, label and #players)
goals.8: Identify the BGP for the NBA Defensive Player of the Year Award (see https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NBA_Defensive_Player_of_the_Year_Award)
goals.9: Consider the players who won the NBA Defensive Player of the Year Award. Return for these players the number of NBA Defensive Player of the Year Award won in their career (the result set must be triples of player IRI, label and #victories)

name: a3121f5139

1.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?name WHERE { wd:Q41421 ?p ?obj . ?p sc:name ?name. } LIMIT 50
SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?property WHERE { wd:Q3665646 ?p ?obj. ?p sc:name ?property. } LIMIT 50
output: Library of Congress Demographic Group Terms ID

2.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?obj ?name WHERE { wd:Q41421 wdt:P641 ?obj . ?obj sc:name ?name. } LIMIT 50
SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?properties WHERE { wd:Q5372 ?p ?obj. ?p sc:name ?properties. } LIMIT 50
output: on focus list of Wikimedia project

3.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?name WHERE { wd:Q3665646 ?p ?o. ?o sc:name ?name. } LIMIT 100
output: Indiana Basketball Hall of Fame ID
Basketball-Reference.com NBA G League player ID
National Collegiate Basketball Hall of Fame ID
Women's Basketball Hall of Fame ID
Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame ID

3.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?properties WHERE { wd:Q13393265 ?p ?obj. ?p sc:name ?properties. } LIMIT 100

4.query: SELECT ?s ?name ?year ?country WHERE { ?s wdt:P31 wd:Q13393265. ?s sc:name ?name. ?s wdt:P17 ?co. ?co sc:name ?country. ?s wdt:P571 ?date. BIND(strbefore(str(?date), "-") AS ?year). FILTER(str(?country) = "France" && str(?year) < "1930"). } ORDER BY DESC(?year) LIMIT 100

SELECT ?s ?name ?year WHERE { ?s wdt:P31 wd:Q13393265. ?s sc:name ?name. ?s wdt:P17 ?co. ?co sc:name ?country. ?s wdt:P571 ?date. BIND(strbefore(str(?date), "-") AS ?year). FILTER(str(?country) = "France" && str(?year) < "1930"). } ORDER BY DESC(?year) LIMIT 100

5.query: SELECT ?s ?name WHERE { ?s wdt:P31 wd:Q27020041. ?s sc:name ?name. FILTER REGEX((?name), "NBA season"). } LIMIT 20
SELECT ?s ?name WHERE { ?s wdt:P31 wd:Q27020041. ?s sc:name ?name. FILTER REGEX((?name), "NBA season"). } ORDER BY ?name LIMIT 20

6.query: SELECT ?o ?name ?o1 ?name1 WHERE { wd:Q41421 wdt:P54 ?o. ?o sc:name ?name. wd:Q25369 wdt:P54 ?o1. ?o1 sc:name ?name1. } LIMIT 50
output: North Carolina Tar Heels men's basketball

6.query: SELECT ?o ?name ?o1 ?name1 WHERE { wd:Q41421 wdt:P54 ?o. ?o sc:name ?name. wd:Q25369 wdt:P54 ?o1. ?o1 sc:name ?name1. } LIMIT 50
output: North Carolina Tar Heels men's basketball

7.query: SELECT ?cont ?continent (count(?s) AS ?Numplayer) WHERE { ?s wdt:P106 wd:Q3665646. ?s sc:name ?name. ?s wdt:P54 ?teams. ?teams sc:name ?team. ?nbateam wdt:P118 wd:Q155223. ?nbateam sc:name ?nba. ?s wdt:P27 ?co. ?co sc:name ?country. ?co wdt:P30 ?cont. ?cont sc:name ?continent. FILTER(?team = ?nba). } GROUP BY ?cont ?continent LIMIT 50

SELECT ?cont ?continent (count(?s) AS ?Numplayer) WHERE { ?s wdt:P106 wd:Q3665646. ?s sc:name ?name. ?s wdt:P54 ?teams. ?teams sc:name ?team. ?nbateam wdt:P118 wd:Q155223. ?nbateam sc:name ?nba. ?s wdt:P27 ?co. ?co sc:name ?country. ?co wdt:P30 ?cont. ?cont sc:name ?continent. FILTER(?team = ?nba). } GROUP BY ?cont ?continent LIMIT 50

output: Laureus World Sports Award for Comeback of the Year
University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill
Associated Press Athlete of the Year
Sports Illustrated Sportsperson of the Year

9.query: SELECT ?o ?name (count(?name) AS ?victories) WHERE { wd:Q845884 wdt:P1346 ?o. ?o sc:name ?name. } GROUP BY ?o ?name LIMIT 100
